      "message": "i think `pageSize \u003e pageSizeMax` would entail the intention more clearly\n\nstepping back, it seems we can reduce repetition by putting specific case first\n\n  case pageSize \u003e pageSizeMax:\n    ...\n  case pageSize \u003c 0:\n    ...\n  default:",
