      "writtenOn": "2019-10-30T02:43:20Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "the benefit of this is in rare cases where actual number of items is dividable by pageSize, we don\u0027t return page token. The cost is that we fetch one more each time.\n\ni think it is cheaper to fetch exactly pageSize and return no pageToken only if we fetched less",
      "range": {
